Their plan was to disqualify our pigeon.

632
00:37:49,081 --> 00:37:52,077
Just shut up. You tell us, Anna.

633
00:37:52,157 --> 00:37:54,397
No matter what,
you should not have beat him.

634
00:37:54,478 --> 00:37:58,450
