come straight to me. - What should I talk?

635
00:37:58,619 --> 00:38:00,689
Hey, tell Anna what you told me.

636
00:38:00,768 --> 00:38:01,798
What did you say?

637
00:38:01,958 --> 00:38:04,663
I said they did not know to
raise pigeons but they threaten.

638
00:38:04,742 --> 00:38:08,288
I was raise between pigeons.
Would I keep mum when he says that?

639
00:38:08,369 --> 00:38:09,592
Would you have kept quiet
if someone said it to you?

640
00:38:09,672 --> 00:38:11,219
I would have slaughtered him.

641
00:38:11,298 --> 00:38:14,782
